{"tid":1452331,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"東鐵線 - 火車車廂電視黑晒，冇播新聞","createTime":"2019-08-12T00:51:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T01:18:53.000Z","uid":52324,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d079506a816863c6c8b2c61a4d881ab55073c6","tid":1452331,"uid":52324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:51:43.000Z","msg":"未知是否牽涉所有列車，但暫時我同幾個朋友今日搭火車都發現車廂冇播新聞。<br />\n<br />\n係咪琴日警察做得太多陰質野!!"},{"pid":"81b6be41adf76cde46dc0ec81c61901a4a833f20","tid":1452331,"uid":294844,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:52:30.000Z","msg":"而家搭緊，有播喎"},{"pid":"1e83d76fdb20530529ff49c6bb54bbc756c3602a","tid":1452331,"uid":134178,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:53:50.000Z","msg":"唔好意思<br />\n借個位<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">812機場見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正式宣佈 &quot;Bruce.Lee&quot; P牌仔係on9<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1451717/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1451717/page/1</a><br />\n佢每一個post都係帶風向叫示威者做無撚用既野、威脅唔到政府既野<br />\n<br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 聽日唔好入機場，係局，係陷阱<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1451252/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1451252/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n-條友好中意深夜帶風向<br />\n-以前開post會有殘體字 (喜恶 痛脚 静坐 绝食)<br />\n-叫義士絕食 (大家都知絕食係玩自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n-已經被人屌過一次五毛、跟住改名 由 &quot;索羅斯&quot; 變 &quot;Bruce.Lee&quot;<br />\n-平時會開正常post，無助大局既post，例如超多個post屌鳩林鄭 <br />\n-唔記得轉ACC講&quot;幫推&quot;<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1443690/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1443690/page/1</a><br />\n知自己柒左跟住唔推post<br />\n<br />\n以前既post：<br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 打死都唔好去離境大堂，記住目的唔係要癱瘓機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434076/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434076/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 【突發】機場和理非行動將有大量警犬着黑衫混入<br />\n事後：機場無事發生過，無見過有鬼<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1426739/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1426739/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好搞TVB呀，和平呼籲佢地罷工啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1422849/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1422849/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 你地繼續叫林鄭下台啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417341/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417341/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1418035/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1418035/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1417281/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1417281/page/1</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1416814/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1416814/page/1</a><br />\n事實：林鄭下台其實都無撚用<br />\n<br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好登報，用啲錢做其他野<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1346745/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1346745/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好成立臨時政府<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1232468/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1232468/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好搞G20登報，搞7.1啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1257157/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1257157/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 唔好沖(殘體字)立法會<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1271370/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1271370/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 五大訴求係on9<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1305986/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1305986/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 警察可能會全面驅趕鄉黑<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1342662/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1342662/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 繼續和平遊行啦~<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1353893/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1353893/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 說服警察加入遊行，感化警察<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1230663/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1230663/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 整多個G牌啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1434492/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1434492/page/1</a><br />\nBruce.Lee [P] : 【急】而家真係需要一個大台<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1337502/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1337502/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nBruce.Lee P牌仔 起底頁面傳送門<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/profile/258370\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/profile/258370</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n推上熱門"},{"pid":"4a6df79d2cecfa0e30478aab810704fa7c4089a7","tid":1452331,"uid":3296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:54:22.000Z","msg":"我坐緊個架都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2205d02e82add1bf26fb8ee4162195bdef1793d4","tid":1452331,"uid":1550,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:54:56.000Z","msg":"頭先搭有播"},{"pid":"b6a3a386cd8d8fc644dfb2842326bea6f0b16356","tid":1452331,"uid":7855,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:55:10.000Z","msg":"有架車係咁<br />\n壞左好撚耐"},{"pid":"71bacf80d1b844a5c41f16d3a944e3ca800b7fbb","tid":1452331,"uid":85193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:55:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"971ad15bf747606c76ab5cc1bf75da3722b36095","tid":1452331,"uid":134061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T00:56:59.000Z","msg":"壞左？有冇聲定靜音車箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d1c3cb62038fc2f7cf578e97b6af4021f9699e30","tid":1452331,"uid":52324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":